<li id="cite_note-37"><b><a href="#cite_ref-37" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.sueddeutsche.de/ausland/artikel/572/69503/print.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sueddeutsche.de/ausland/artikel/572/69503/print.html" rel="nofollow">Im Schattenreich der Krake</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/S%C3%BCddeutsche_Zeitung" title="Süddeutsche Zeitung">Süddeutsche Zeitung</a></i>, 3 February 2006. <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(German)</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-38"><b><a href="#cite_ref-38" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFWeb_Editor2006">Web Editor (2006-03-28). <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20071013095517/http://italymag.co.uk/2006/news-from-italy/current-affairs/mafia-drugs-submarine-seized/" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20071013095517/http://italymag.co.uk/2006/news-from-italy/current-affairs/mafia-drugs-submarine-seized/" rel="nofollow">"Mafia drugs submarine seized"</a>. <i>News From Italy</i>. Italy Magazine. Archived from <a href="http://www.italymag.co.uk/2006/news-from-italy/current-affairs/mafia-drugs-submarine-seized/" class="external text" title="http://www.italymag.co.uk/2006/news-from-italy/current-affairs/mafia-drugs-submarine-seized/" rel="nofollow">the original</a> on 2007-10-13<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20071013095517/http://italymag.co.uk/2006/news-from-italy/current-affairs/mafia-drugs-submarine-seized/" class="external free" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20071013095517/http://italymag.co.uk/2006/news-from-italy/current-affairs/mafia-drugs-submarine-seized/" rel="nofollow">http://web.archive.org/web/20071013095517/http://italymag.co.uk/2006/news-from-italy/current-affairs/mafia-drugs-submarine-seized/</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-02-03</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Mafia+drugs+submarine+seized&amp;rft.atitle=News+From+Italy&amp;rft.aulast=Web+Editor&amp;rft.au=Web+Editor&amp;rft.date=2006-03-28&amp;rft.pub=Italy+Magazine&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20071013095517%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fitalymag.co.uk%2F2006%2Fnews-from-italy%2Fcurrent-affairs%2Fmafia-drugs-submarine-seized%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:%27Ndrangheta"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-39"><b><a href="#cite_ref-39" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/6970067.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/6970067.stm" rel="nofollow">"Mafia suspects arrested in Italy."</a> <i>BBC News</i>. August 30, 2007.</li>
</ol>
</div>
